::KitKat::

She smiled at Drillbit, glad that he was safe and sound. "We have 
company.  This is Cyber Claw." motioning to her with her hand. "And 
Black Aracnia will arrive shortly. We are going to talk of an 
allience between our two groups.  Possably uniting all the pred 
groups.  But for now, we shall focus on just our two groups."  She 
smiled up at Starscream and then back at Drillbit.
